{"id": 1837, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x戴森】吹个头发，你会纠结多少事情？", "description": "我就想愉快的吹个头。", "record_count": 9048, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170805183837jneKRi6JcSMW1Nly.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-06T02:08:41Z", "options": [{"id": 227584, "content": "吹头发？死宅没有这个需求(｡ŏ_ŏ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047703}, {"id": 227840, "content": "哇我怎么这么美", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091016}, {"id": 227585, "content": "怎么吹 \n用冷风热风 \n全干还是半干", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927303}, {"id": 227586, "content": "太热了，什么时候能吹好\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 176, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079794}, {"id": 228098, "content": "想赶紧吹干睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099682}, {"id": 227587, "content": "老担心头发掉太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 410, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039999}, {"id": 227843, "content": "每次吹的时候都觉得要热死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098638}, {"id": 227588, "content": "啊啊啊啊啊啊澡白洗了 又出一身汗\n啊啊啊啊啊啊好重好热\n啊啊啊啊啊啊好累\n。。\n行了 \n就这样吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 340, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028146}, {"id": 228100, "content": "就吹冷风吧\r\n慢点就慢点\r\n总比吹热风热死强", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050415}, {"id": 230148, "content": "洗发精的香味散失掉了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107687}, {"id": 227845, "content": "下次再涂头发精油?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098658}, {"id": 227590, "content": "每次吹头发都想好浪费时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 735, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098096}, {"id": 227846, "content": "赶紧吹完睡觉啊 不想有黑眼圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002514}, {"id": 227591, "content": "吹了干得爆燥，不吹塌得油腻", "image": null, "praise_count": 195, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648014}, {"id": 227847, "content": "既想吹的有层次，结果吹歪了，重新再洗一遍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849168}, {"id": 228103, "content": "吹啊吹啊，怕我吹得骄傲放纵", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008853}, {"id": 227592, "content": "掉头发啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊我会不会秃头", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296767}, {"id": 227848, "content": "吹头发伤害头发，还是不吹了。如果有急事要急着出门就必须吹", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857424}, {"id": 230408, "content": "脸会被吹干，吹的缺水?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108724}, {"id": 227593, "content": "吹完头发对着镜子用手捋一捋，感觉自己真TM帅呆了（或者美爆了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 271561}, {"id": 228618, "content": "这是造型师吹的不是真的，我自己能吹成什么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1101734}, {"id": 227595, "content": "敷面膜的时候吹头发面膜都吹干了", "image": null, "praise_count": 162, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098100}, {"id": 227596, "content": "难道只有我一人是不吹头发的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890598}, {"id": 231436, "content": "用热风太烫用常温风太慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113727}, {"id": 227854, "content": "啊  能干完吗 我还有时间洗澡吗 还有多久熄灯 ??", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092951}, {"id": 227600, "content": "反正都回干，催，会有用？", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821564}, {"id": 227601, "content": "吹完炸毛", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773277}, {"id": 227857, "content": "你每次吹得是头还是发？\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230786}, {"id": 227602, "content": "容易干时不吹，不容易干时吹一会，个人觉得经常吹不咋地\n\n\n\n我是短发^0^", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 231698, "content": "我那可爱的小屋檐刘海", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 227603, "content": "这大热天，都是用电风扇吹干的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050597}, {"id": 227604, "content": "啥玩应?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098156}, {"id": 227860, "content": "想让别人给我吹头发，自己美美哒享受就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983509}, {"id": 227605, "content": "时间太久 举着累", "image": null, "praise_count": 213, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098158}, {"id": 227606, "content": "夏天吹头发…用热风越吹越热越干不了…用冷风越吹越冷怕感冒…不知道是头发太多…还是吹风机不好用…?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 175977}, {"id": 227862, "content": "大夏天吹头。热死。吹完一头汗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 228118, "content": "每次吹完头发，发觉又该洗澡了捎带脚把头发也得冲一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802507}, {"id": 227607, "content": "不吹，自然干(๑˙ー˙๑)", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080730}, {"id": 228119, "content": "本来头发就多、厚、干燥，越吹发质越干", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674780}, {"id": 235287, "content": "不该翘的地方翘起来了 不该长的地方长长了 。。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945691}, {"id": 227608, "content": "吹翘了怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093426}, {"id": 227864, "content": "夏天真的是难过\n吹了，跟没洗一样\n不吹，又湿哒哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1309076}, {"id": 227609, "content": "一天隔一天洗头店，不存在！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670012}, {"id": 228121, "content": "就觉得自己是一个众望所归的洗剪吹", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099025}, {"id": 227610, "content": "吹头发辐射好大?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052105}, {"id": 227866, "content": "在傍晚的疲惫中疲惫的洗澡又疲惫的吹头发更疲惫的睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082191}, {"id": 227611, "content": "每次吹就想剃光", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75269}, {"id": 227867, "content": "我就想把头发刮了，成光头。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092571}, {"id": 227612, "content": "时间太长", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169464}, {"id": 227870, "content": "没吹好，怎么办！再洗一遍，重吹吧！好麻烦啊，然后就在纠结中放弃了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305549}]}